<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset='utf-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <title>Verify Your Email - PokeRanking</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #f5f5f5;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
      }
      .header {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #EE1515 0%, #C00000 100%);
        padding: 40px 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .header h1 {
        color: #ffffff;
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 32px;
        font-weight: 700;
        text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      }
      .header p {
        color: #ffffff;
        margin: 10px 0 0 0;
        font-size: 16px;
        opacity: 0.95;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 40px 30px;
      }
      .greeting {
        font-size: 18px;
        color: #333;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .message {
        font-size: 16px;
        color: #555;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
        line-height: 1.8;
      }
      .code-container {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FFD700 0%, #FFA500 100%);
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 30px;
        text-align: center;
        margin: 30px 0;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.3);
      }
      .code-label {
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #333;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }
      .code {
        font-size: 48px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #C00000;
        letter-spacing: 8px;
        font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
        text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      .divider {
        text-align: center;
        margin: 30px 0;
        color: #999;
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 600;
      }
      .divider::before,
      .divider::after {
        content: '';
        display: inline-block;
        width: 80px;
        height: 1px;
        background-color: #ddd;
        vertical-align: middle;
        margin: 0 15px;
      }
      .button-container {
        text-align: center;
        margin: 30px 0;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 16px 40px;
        background-color: #3B7DDD;
        color: #ffffff;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 8px;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 16px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(59, 125, 221, 0.3);
        transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
      }
      .button:hover {
        background-color: #2563EB;
      }
      .note {
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #777;
        margin-top: 30px;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
        border-left: 4px solid #FFD700;
        border-radius: 4px;
      }
      .footer {
        background-color: #f5f5f5;
        padding: 30px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #666;
      }
      .footer p {
        margin: 5px 0;
      }
      .footer a {
        color: #3B7DDD;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
        .content {
          padding: 30px 20px;
        }
        .code {
          font-size: 36px;
          letter-spacing: 6px;
        }
        .button {
          padding: 14px 30px;
          font-size: 15px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='container'>
      <div class='header'>
        <h1>ðŸŽ® Welcome to PokeRanking!</h1>
        <p>Catch 'em all and rank your favorites</p>
      </div>

      <div class='content'>
        <div class='greeting'>
          <strong>Hello, {{name}}!</strong>
        </div>

        <div class='message'>
          Thank you for joining PokeRanking! You're one step away from ranking
          your favorite PokÃ©mon. To complete your registration and activate your
          account, please verify your email address.
        </div>

        <div class='code-container'>
          <div class='code-label'>Your Verification Code</div>
          <div class='code'>{{code}}</div>
        </div>

        <div class='message' style='text-align: center; margin-top: 20px;'>
          Enter this code on the verification page to activate your account.
        </div>

        <div class='divider'>OR</div>

        <div class='button-container'>
          <a href='{{verificationUrl}}' class='button'>Verify Email Address</a>
        </div>

        <div class='note'>
          <strong>ðŸ”’ Security Note:</strong>
          This verification code will expire in 24 hours. If you didn't create
          an account with PokeRanking, you can safely ignore this email.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class='footer'>
        <p><strong>PokeRanking</strong></p>
        <p>Â© {{year}} PokeRanking. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>This email was sent to <strong>{{email}}</strong></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
